    "description": "Set next to a private section of Kleopatra Beach along the Mediterranean Sea, this down-to-earth hotel is 4 km from Alanya Castle, a Seljuk-era fortress, and 44 km from Gazipaşa Airport.\n The unassuming rooms feature private balconies, Wi-Fi access and flat-screen TVs; some have sea views. Room service is offered.\n Breakfast and dinner are served in a buffet restaurant that has terrace seating. There's a casual lobby bar, a spa and a gym, as well as 2 outdoor pools (1 for kids), a hot tub and a poolside bar. Table games and regular entertainment are provided. Water sports, tennis, basketball and volleyball are available.",
    "info": "Informal hotel offering a private section of beach, plus a buffet eatery, a spa ",
