    "description": "Across the road from Gulhane Park in the Old Town, this upmarket hotel in an Ottoman mansion is a 4-minute walk from Marmaray Sirkeci train station and 10 minutes on foot from the mosaics of the Hagia Sophia museum.\n Warmly decorated rooms provide Wi-Fi, flat-screens, safes and minifridges, plus tea and coffeemakers. Family rooms have pull-out sofas or are composed of 2 rooms. Upgraded rooms add whirlpool tubs; some feature balconies with park views.\n There's an elegant restaurant with chandeliers and a cozy bar, and a terrace featuring park views. A spa has an indoor pool, a sauna, a Turkish bath and a gym. Tours and cooking classes are offered.",
