    "description": "In a stately building with a 6-story atrium, this polished hotel in the harborfront Eminönü district is a 5-minute walk from Marmaray Sirkeci train station, 6 minutes' walk from the historic Spice Bazaar and 2 km from the 15th-century Topkapı Palace.\n Featuring crown moldings and tufted headboards, the snug, elegant rooms provide flat-screen TVs, Wi-Fi access and minifridges. Upgraded rooms add tea and coffeemakers, and/or sitting areas. Room service is available 24/7.\n Dining options include a cafe with a patio, and a chic restaurant offering a glass-enclosed dining room, panoramic city views and outdoor seating. Breakfast is also available.",
